1.Why do we convert continuous values into categories
  To make data easier to understand and analyze. Instead of dealing with many numeric values, we group them into meaningful labels like Gold, Silver, and Bronze.

2.What is the difference between business segmentation and technical bucketing
  Business segmentation is based on predefined business rules such as spend greater than 100 being labeled as Gold.
  Technical bucketing is based on data distribution or algorithms such as quantiles or bucketizer.
